# Thin vertical slices

- Build complete loops end-to-end, then deepen each layer.
- Do not overbuild: prefer the smallest useful slice that proves the path.
- Phase 0/1 scope: public-safe repo + minimal Mastra runtime only.
- Defer Chief of Staff, delegation, job queues, Obsidian, scheduling, authoring agents, and the full skill system.
- Code for deterministic work; LLMs for judgment.
